{
  "id": "adv_card_rui_06_03",
  "title": "天動瑠依 3話 大切な人に想いを",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_toffice_night",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "私には……やらなければいけないことがあるので",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have something I need to take care of.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（瑠依……こんなに真剣な顔をしてどうしたんだ？）\n（それに、優もすみれも抜きで、話だなんて）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Rui… Why is she seemed so serious ?）\n（And she's talking without Yu and Sumire…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "私は覚悟を決めてきました。今日こそは……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've made up my mind. Today‚ I will…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "る、瑠依？　じりじりと近づかれると\nもの凄く怖いんだが……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Rui? When you approach so seriously‚\nit's terrifying…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9133.333333300001,
          "startTime": 34.5333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11766.666666700004,
          "startTime": 37.1666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3666.666666700003,
          "startTime": 29.0666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6500,
          "startTime": 31.9
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14433.3333333,
          "startTime": 39.8333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-call-01.m4a",
          "delay": 17033.3333333,
          "startTime": 42.4333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "私、{user}さんに\n渡したい、物……が……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There's something\nI want to give… you…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "またしてもすまない……\n相手は……三枝さんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Once again‚ I'm sorry…\nThe other one is…Saegusa-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "どうぞ、出て下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ come in.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6666.666666599994,
          "startTime": 44.3333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14799.999999999996,
          "startTime": 52.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ……もしもし\nえ？　分かりました、ぜひ……はい、はい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh… hello?\nHuh? I see‚ understood.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事の話ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Is it about work?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや……「めずらしく朝倉と飲んでるから\nお前も来ないか」って、誘われたんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… He invited me‚ saying‚\n\"I'm unusually drinking with Asakura‚ so why don't you come too?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "え、パパ……朝倉社長が？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh‚ Papa… President Asakura?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "くぅぅ～……っ、よりによって……っ！\nもう、もう……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… Come on…!\nGeez‚ seriously…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "パパ……恨むわ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll hold a grudge against Papa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "えぇっと……瑠依？　それで、さっきの話なんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ well… Rui? So‚ about what you were talking about earlier…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "もういいです\nそんな気分じゃありませんから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm done with that.\nI'm not in the mood for it anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、お二人が待ってるんですから\n早く行った方がいいんじゃないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ the both of them are waiting‚\nso you should go quickly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ yeah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "どうぞ、朝まで飲んだくれて下さい\nゴミ捨て場で寝ないようにして下さいね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please‚ enjoy drinking until morning.\nJust don't end up sleeping in the trash dumpster‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで酷いことにはならないぞ！？\n……多分だけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It won't be that bad!\nProbably…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "当日までに渡すチャンスは……まだあるわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There'd be still a chance to give it before the day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "別に当日でもいいけど……\nううん、やっぱり変に意識してしまいそう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's fine even not on the day itself‚ but…\nNo‚ I might end up overly conscious…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui015.m4a",
      "text": "あ……でも、もしかしたら今のこの気持ちも\n新曲を歌う時の糧になるかも……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… but maybe this feeling right now\ncould be the source of inspiration when singing the new song…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依？　さっきからどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui? What's wrong with you lately?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui016.m4a",
      "text": "なんでもないですよ。気を付けて行って来て下さいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's nothing. Please be careful on your way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――バレンタインスペシャルライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――バレンタインスペシャルライブ当日",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5799.999999999983,
          "startTime": 136.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui017.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん\nトリエルのバレンタインライブはいかがでしたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚\nHow was TRINITYAiLE's Valentine's live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui018.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you very much.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_musicprogram-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "musicprogram-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rui_06_03-rui019.m4a",
      "text": "この曲が少しでもみなさんの心に響いて……\n大事な一歩を踏み出す後押しが出来たら嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
